    "## üéØ Risk Taking as a Delegate\n",
    "\n",
    "When you're a **fund manager** investing on behalf of others, your evaluation criteria shift:\n",
    "\n",
    "| **Evaluation Metric** | **Description** | **Impact on Strategy** |\n",
    "|:---------------------|:---------------|:----------------------|\n",
    "| üìä **Benchmark Performance** | Returns relative to index | Forces benchmark-aware positioning |\n",
    "| üìâ **Short-term Volatility** | Daily/monthly fluctuations | Limits aggressive strategies |\n",
    "| üòä **Client Satisfaction** | Redemption risk | Influences communication & transparency |\n",
    "\n",
    "### ‚ö†Ô∏è **The Stop-Loss Reality**\n",
    "\n",
    "Every delegate faces an implicit or explicit **stop-loss rule**:\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "if portfolio_loss > threshold:\n",
    "    liquidate_positions()\n",
    "    manager.terminate()\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**Critical considerations:**\n",
    "- üÜï New managers face tighter stop-losses\n",
    "- üìù Stop-loss may be explicit (stated by principal)\n",
    "- üë• More often implicit (investor panic threshold)\n",
    "- ‚ö° **Investing without knowing this number is reckless!**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### üìä **Principal vs. Delegate: Key Differences**\n",
    "\n",
    "| **Perspective** | **Risk Tolerance** | **Goal** | **Constraints** |\n",
    "|:---------------|:------------------|:---------|:---------------|\n",
    "| **üë§ Principal** | Personal | Maximize lifetime utility | Few (internal) |\n",
    "| **üè¢ Delegate** | Institutional | Maximize performance within mandate | Many (external) |\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### ‚úÖ **Knowledge Check**\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style=\"background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n",
    "\n",
    "**Question**: Why might a delegate choose a lower-risk portfolio than a principal?\n",
    "\n",
    "<details>\n",
    "<summary>üîç Click to reveal answer</summary>\n",
    "\n",
    "Delegates face external constraints and career risks. Their incentives often penalize short-term underperformance, leading them to reduce exposure to volatility‚Äîeven if it means lower expected returns.\n",
    "\n",
    "</details>\n",
    "</div>\n",
